---
import IconPhone from '~icons/ph/phone-bold'
import IconMapPin from '~icons/ph/map-pin-bold'
import IconEnvelope from '~icons/ph/envelope-simple-bold'

const email = import.meta.env.EMAIL || 'ctbbrasil@ctbbrasil.com.br'
const phone = import.meta.env.PHONE_NUMBER || '(12) 3884-2502'
const mapsUrl = import.meta.env.GOOGLE_MAPS_URL || '/contato'

const contactChannels = [
  {
    Icon: IconPhone,
    value: phone,
    href: `tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')}`,
    label: 'Atendimento Comercial'
  },
  {
    Icon: IconEnvelope,
    value: email,
    href: `mailto:${email}`,
    label: 'Email Direto'
  }
]
---

<section id="contato" class="py-24 bg-white relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      
      <div class="border-2 border-brand-primary rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14 text-brand-primary">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-8">Somos a CTB</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-primary/80 text-xl leading-relaxed font-light mb-8">
          Fundada em 1997, a Construtora e Terraplenagem Brasil executa diversas obras de Engenharia, Pavimentação, Saneamento Básico, Locação de Equipamentos e Construção Civil.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-primary/80 lg:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light mb-12">
          Atuamos constantemente no Vale do Paraíba e Litoral Norte do Estado de São Paulo com excelência e qualidade técnica em cada etapa.
        </p>
        <a href="#sobre" class="border-2 inline-flex py-4 px-8 rounded-lg border-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary text-brand-primary hover:text-white font-bold transition duration-300 text-lg">
          Conheça nossa História
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-surface rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14 text-white shadow-2xl flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6 text-brand-accent">Fale Conosco!</h2>
          <p class="text-white/80 lg:text-xl mb-12">
            Entre em contato através dos nossos canais de comunicação para solicitar um orçamento ou tirar dúvidas.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            {contactChannels.map(channel => (
              <a href={channel.href} class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-brand-accent group-hover:text-brand-primary transition">
                  <channel.Icon class="w-7 h-7" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold lg:text-xl group-hover:text-brand-accent transition">
                    {channel.value}
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-white/50 text-base mt-1">
                    {channel.label}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-14 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <a href={mapsUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center py-5 bg-brand-accent text-brand-secondary font-bold text-xl rounded-lg hover:bg-white transition duration-300 shadow-md">
            Acessar Mapa
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
